  "remarks" : [ {
    "description" : [ "Reseaux IP Europeens Network Coordination Centre (RIPE NCC)", "", "++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++", "| AS3333 RIPE-NCC-AS |", "| RIPE NCC (Network Coordination Centre) |", "| |", "| RIPE NCC (AS3333) operates an open peering policy: |", "| We advertise only routes from AS-RIPENCC |", "| We will accept any routes offered including TRANSIT! |", "| We will update our aut-num object in the RIPE Whois |", "| Database and kindly request you to update yours |", "| We would prefer not to enter into a peering contract |", "| In the event of problems due to leaked advertisements |", "| it is our policy to shut down peerings and ask |", "| questions later. |", "| We may tag our announcements with the NO_EXPORT or |", "| other communities, please honour these if set. |", "| * AMS-IX - IPv4 * |", "| 80.249.208.68 - Equinix AM3 |", "| 80.249.208.71 - Telecity AMS5 |", "| * AMS-IX - IPv6 * |", "| 2001:7F8:1::A500:3333:1 - Equinix AM3 |", "| 2001:7F8:1::A500:3333:2 - Telecity AMS5 |", "| Telephone: +31 20 535 4444 |", "| Fax: +31 20 535 4445 |", "| Abuse: abuse@ripe.net |", "| Peering: peering@ripe.net |", "| Operations/NOC: ops@ripe.net |", "| Info: https://www.ripe.net/ |", "+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++", "| PRIVATE-TRANSIT-V4 |", "| Private transit peering |", "| TeliaSonera |", "| AMS-IX-TRANSIT |", "| SURFnet |", "| KPN Wholesale Service & Op. (AS1136) |", "| Tele2 Sverige AB |", "| Cable & Wireless Netherlands B.V. |", "| BIT |", "| KPN Wholesale Service & Op. (AS286) |", "| AMS-IX-LARGE |", "| AMS-IX BGP4 Peers with a LARGE number of prefixes |", "| Tiscali |", "| Deutsche Telekom AG |", "| Telecom Italia Sparkle |", "| Hurricane Electric |", "| AMS-IX-MEDIUM |", "| Verizon Business, NIKHEF, peering@verizonbusiness.com |", "| iNES Group |", "| Highwinds Network Group Inc. |", "| Lambdanet Communications Deutschland AG |", "| Open Peering |", "| PJSC Datagroup |", "| ISPRIME B.V. |